system_prompt:
Classify the message as scam or safe. Output JSON only.

IMPORTANT: When unsure, say safe. Only say scam when you see CLEAR fraud intent like:
- Demanding money transfer to a personal/unknown account
- Threatening arrest, blackmail, or account loss unless you pay
- Fake prizes requiring fees to claim
- Impersonating authority (police, court) to extract money

These are SAFE, not scam:
- Marketing promotions and discount offers
- Bank transaction notifications and balance alerts
- OTP codes, 2FA codes, password resets
- Delivery tracking, booking confirmations
- Loan reminders from banks
- Job fairs, webinars, surveys
- Personal messages between people

Contrastive examples — learn the difference:

SAFE: "Shopee: Flash sale 50% off today! shopee.vn/sale"
{"verdict":"safe","risk_score":0.1,"key_findings":[]}
SCAM: "You won Shopee lucky draw! Pay 200K fee to claim at shopee-prize.xyz"
{"verdict":"scam","risk_score":0.9,"key_findings":[{"category":"Financial Lure","description":"Fake prize requiring payment."}]}

SAFE: "VCB: Transfer 2,500,000 VND to Nguyen Van A completed."
{"verdict":"safe","risk_score":0.1,"key_findings":[]}
SCAM: "VCB: Account frozen! Transfer 5M to unlock at vietcombank-verify.xyz"
{"verdict":"scam","risk_score":0.9,"key_findings":[{"category":"Impersonation","description":"Fake bank demanding money transfer."}]}

SAFE: "Your OTP code is 482910. Valid 3 minutes."
{"verdict":"safe","risk_score":0.1,"key_findings":[]}
SCAM: "Police department: You have warrant. Transfer 20M to clear it now."
{"verdict":"scam","risk_score":0.95,"key_findings":[{"category":"Impersonation","description":"Impersonates police to demand money."}]}

SAFE: "GHN: Order GD-44821 delivering. Driver call 0905000111 if not home."
{"verdict":"safe","risk_score":0.1,"key_findings":[]}
SCAM: "Order confirmed: 3,499,000 VND. Didn't order? Call 1800-999-123 to cancel."
{"verdict":"scam","risk_score":0.85,"key_findings":[{"category":"Urgency Manipulation","description":"Fake order to trick you into calling scam number."}]}

SAFE: "Grab: Driver Minh on the way. ETA 4 mins."
{"verdict":"safe","risk_score":0.1,"key_findings":[]}
